metadata.description:
The guy meets an ethereal fairytale creature combing his hair on the riverbank. Struck by the beauty he takes the magic comb. But heathen spirits will not forgive the theft easily. How long will it take man to reckon for his weakness?

The comb is an artifact from the fashion film "Yooha"
